    "title": "Choosing a StoreKit API for In-App Purchases"
  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The StoreKit framework provides two APIs to implement a store in your app and offer in-app purchases:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.storekit/documentation/StoreKit/in-app-purchase",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " is a Swift-based API that provides App Store-signed transactions in JSON Web Signature (JWS) format, available starting in iOS 15, macOS 12, tvOS 15, watchOS 8, and visionOS 1.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.storekit/documentation/StoreKit/original-api-for-in-app-purchase",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " provides transaction information using App Store receipts, available starting in iOS 3, macOS 10.7, tvOS 9, watchOS 6.2, and visionOS 1.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "The ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.storekit/documentation/StoreKit/original-api-for-in-app-purchase",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "type": "reference"
                },
                {
                  "text": " is deprecated.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "Note",
          "style": "note",
          "type": "aside"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "If your app has a minimum required operating system that the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.storekit/documentation/StoreKit/in-app-purchase",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " API supports, use this API to take advantage of Swift concurrency and simplified in-app purchase workflows. Use this API for visionOS apps that use multiple scenes.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Use the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.storekit/documentation/StoreKit/original-api-for-in-app-purchase",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " to maintain and update app versions that have a minimum required operating system of the following versions: macOS 11 or earlier, iOS 14 or earlier, iPadOS 14 or earlier, tvOS 14 or earlier, or watchOS 7 or earlier.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "An app can use both the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.storekit/documentation/StoreKit/in-app-purchase",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " API and the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.storekit/documentation/StoreKit/original-api-for-in-app-purchase",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " if the app runs in iOS 15, macOS 12, tvOS 15, watchOS 8, and visionOS 1 or later. However, only the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.storekit/documentation/StoreKit/in-app-purchase",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " API supports multi-scene apps for visionOS.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Both APIs provide access to your data in the App Store, such as your configured in-app purchases and transaction information for your customers. In-app purchases that users make using either API are fully available to both APIs.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Use-the-In-App-Purchase-API-to-access-new-features",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Use the In-App Purchase API to access new features",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The following features are available only with the Swift-based ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.storekit/documentation/StoreKit/in-app-purchase",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " APIs:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.storekit/documentation/StoreKit/storekit-views",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", which provide the UI to build a store in your app",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Refund request sheets, such as ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.storekit/documentation/StoreKit/Transaction/beginRefundRequest(for:in:)-65tph",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", that enable customers to request refunds",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Information about a subscriptionâ€™s renewal status, such as auto-renew preferences. For more information, see ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.storekit/documentation/StoreKit/Product/SubscriptionInfo/Status-swift.struct",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Information about available promotional offers and a subscriberâ€™s eligibility for an introductory offer. For more information, see ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.storekit/documentation/StoreKit/Product/SubscriptionInfo",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Deferring or suppressing Billing Issue messages that the system displays. For more information, see ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.storekit/documentation/StoreKit/Message",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Presenting the App Store sheet for managing subscriptions. For more information, see ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.storekit/documentation/StoreKit/AppStore/showManageSubscriptions(in:subscriptionGroupID:)",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Transaction information in JSON Web Signature (JWS) format. For more information, see ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.storekit/documentation/StoreKit/Transaction",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Use-the-Original-API-to-support-certain-features",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Use the Original API to support certain features",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You might need to use the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.storekit/documentation/StoreKit/original-api-for-in-app-purchase",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " for the following features, if your app supports them:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Promoting in-app purchases in apps that run in iOS 11 through 16.3. For more informaton, see ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.storekit/documentation/StoreKit/promoting-in-app-purchases",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". For information about this feature in iOS 16.4, see ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.storekit/documentation/StoreKit/supporting-promoted-in-app-purchases-in-your-app",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "The Volume Purchase Program (VPP). For more information, see ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/DeviceManagement",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
